  "name": "Building Blocks - OGC Building Blocks for DCAT-AP-NL 3.0 - EXPERIMENTAL",
  "abstract": "These building blocks are an experimental implementation of DCAT-AP-NL.\n",
  "description": "The purpose of this collection is to experiment with the building block approach and to showcase how\nthis potentially can add value.\n\nNote: the building blocks in the geonovum repository are a more conservative implementation while the \nbuilding blocks in this repository are more experimental.\n",
  "modified": "2026-07-02T08:04:55.309951",
